
Web Applicatian developed as a pet project, fully functional you can play with your friends just join the same room and type the command /start
Languages and Technologies used:

Javascript
Node.js
Heroku
Express
SocketIO
MustacheJS
HTML
CSS
Heroku Link: https://murmuring-cliffs-98203.herokuapp.com/

To run this app in your localhost:

Make sure you have Node.js configured in your computer
Clone the app
Open the terminal and go to the app folder
Type the command npm install
Type node server.js or npm start to run the app
Open in your browser the URL localhost:3000
